s of whether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/49978/', '', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Cetirizine, Trimethobenzamide, Azelastine', 'Ginkgo biloba, Aducanumab', 1767369485);
